{"tid":131512,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電視收購本地 Groupon 業務  全力進軍網購市場？","createTime":"2017-02-23T06:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T07:31:42.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c59ddd49aa957d651266d92e8bb29ce20022277e","tid":131512,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"香港電視以 US$67.1 萬（約 HK$521 萬），向賣方 Groupon Inc. 收購 Shift Media 全部已發行股本，將藉著 Groupon 以電子折扣優惠券供應貨品及服務的方式優勢，進軍團購優惠券銷售行業，以及加強於網上市場行業之領導地位。據本地《經濟通》報道，香港電視受惠收購 Groupon 本地電子商貿業務刺激，今早股價再升 2.68%，報 HK$1.53。<br />\n<br />\n如此一來，是否意味香港電視專心做好網購？說好的免費電視台呢，何時有數可找？"},{"pid":"de1ea0481e8b593548a335bb15653741845ba48d","tid":131512,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"Wiki好波"},{"pid":"448ad41b646f34d11b5046f8c9df4668649694aa","tid":131512,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾買垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c7411149d4d61989dfeb9ac741fcf58d5ae8da","tid":131512,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:48:49.000Z","msg":"hktv冇tv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f7ef9d3356ff9b20427fab759b1774bb51adb5","tid":131512,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b866f68a16660239ad6026efd48bb8a5e5492b55","tid":131512,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"689唔發牌點找數？"},{"pid":"47068187f53d6d4531ee1d8a67febe47c0c3a7b5","tid":131512,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"供股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc44d46a9a48407f4002dd20845a987c53cd4964","tid":131512,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23